<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <h4>{{t "Supervisors" key="supervisors"}}</h4>
</div>
<div class='col-sm-12'>
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Communication grows faster with a team. Add the people who support your communicator — family, teachers, therapists — so everyone stays connected." key="supervisors_explainer"}}</li>
    {{#if this.setup_user.supporter_role}}
      <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "To access boards and reports, communicators need to add you as a supervisor from their dashboard." key="get_added_as_supervisor"}}</li>
    {{else}}
      <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Supervisor accounts are free — invite your team to sign up and add them here." key="add_lots_of_supervisors"}}</li>
    {{/if}}
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Once added, supervisors can view and practice with the communicator's boards on their own devices — great for building confidence with the vocabulary." key="supervisors_2"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Supervisors with editing permission can also add new buttons and phrases to help the communicator grow." key="supervisors_3"}}</li>
  </ul>
  {{#unless this.setup_user.supporter_role}}
    {{#if this.setup_user}}
      <p style='margin-top: 20px;'><button class='btn btn-default btn-lg' {{action "manage_supervision"}}>
        {{t "Add or Manage Supervisors" key="add_of_manage_supervisors"}}
      </button></p>
    {{/if}}
  {{/unless}}
</div>
